 geometries, relaxing the\nrequirements on mesh quality introduced by existing finite volume solvers and\nalleviating the need for time-consuming manual procedures for mesh generation\nto be performed by specialised technicians.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2022 19:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Dec 2022 17:05:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-13"}
