e, depression, attention deficit hyperactivity\ndisorder and headache disorders. The results demonstrate its effectiveness and\ngeneralizability for multiple brain diseases diagnosis with multimodal\nfeatures. BrainFormer may promote precision of neuroimaging-based diagnosis in\nclinical practice and motivate future studies on fMRI analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2022 07:54:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2022 05:41:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 06:54:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
